(go-to: "Epilogue")
]
]
(else:)[You read it twice. The second time, you notice the line //"the flag is in the system. The grade is in the system."// That's where your flag is, too. That's where your appeal, if you file one, will land.

You weren't the first. You won't be the last.

(link: "Appeal. Send them your Google Doc version history as proof.")[
